init_text: Your entire life, you've been told you're deathly allergic to bees. You've always had people protecting you from them, be it your mother or a hired hand. Today, one slips through and lands on your shoulder. You hear a tiny voice say "Your Majesty, what are your orders?"

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "I don't know what you're talking about, I'm deathly allergic to bees.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You are taken aback by this, but then you notice the bee is moving away from you.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The cave is dark, but you can see the walls are covered in carvings.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: As you walk through the cave, you begin to understand what the carvings are.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: What you find next causes you to freeze in your tracks.
